    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "MILES, Wash, Dec %. - About\n$50 adult Indians have agreed to\nopen the Colville reservation for\nsettlement. Maj. James McLaugh-\nlin let the news out a few days\nago. The agreement, which must\nbe ratified by congress, includes\nthe payment of 1000 900 to Indians\nfor land already coded on the north\nhalf."
    }
